/Economic%20impacts%20of%20marine%20litter%20KIMO.pdf</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> Galgani et al (2000) </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">‘</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Litter on the Sea Floor Along European Coasts</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">’, </span><a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/0025326X"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; text-decoration:underline">Marine Pollution Bulletin</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/0025326X/40/6"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">40 </span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">(</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">6</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">)</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">,</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">pp. </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">516</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">–</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">527</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0025326X99002349"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0025326X99002349</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn13"></a><a href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><a href="http://www.mcsuk.org/downloads/pollution/beachwatch/latest2011/Methods%20&amp;%20Results%20BW10.pdf"><span style="color:#00